name: The Yellow Monkey: Trancemission VJ Remix
overview: The Yellow Monkey - Trancemission VJ Remix is a data disc about music video clips and discography of the rock band. - Trancemission VJ: Interact with the music video - Trancemission Guide: Data and production staff credits of the game. - The Yellow Monkey Clips: Features 8 different music videos - The Yellow Monkey Discography.
